# Base exclusions (from .dockerignore)
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
.git/
.github/
dist/
**/dist/
.angular/
**/.angular/
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.test.ts
**/e2e/
coverage/
**/coverage/
.env*
.vscode/
.idea/
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
docs/
*.md
!README.md

# Coolify/local: single context for all services; each Dockerfile COPYs only what it needs.
# Service-specific dockerignore.* files exist for CI if you reintroduce build-and-push.
